      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is best suited for someone looking for a reliable budget commuter or a secondary work car. The exterior has several noticeable scuffs and the paint is fading on the hood, while the interior shows clear signs of use including some staining on the upholstery and wear on the steering wheel. Mechanically, it starts and runs, though it will likely need some routine maintenance and minor repairs in the near future to keep it in peak operating shape. It is a solid, honest car that gets the job done without any frills.",
