    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, there's not a single scratch or dent to be found, and the interior is absolutely spotless. It drives like a total dream! I'm really sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
