    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade specimen that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This vehicle features a flawless exterior finish with a deep, mirror-like luster, completely free of swirls, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of pristine leather and untouched trim, retaining that unmistakable factory-fresh scent. Every mechanical component has been meticulously maintained, offering a driving experience that is tight, responsive, and whisper-quiet. From the spotless engine bay to the unmarked alloy wheels, no detail has been overlooked. This is a rare opportunity to own a perfectly preserved example for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
