    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't find another one like this. This beauty has been my absolute pride and joy, and it shows\u2014it's in absolutely flawless condition! I've kept it tucked away in the garage, babied it every single day, and it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for a new home. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
