    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a showroom-grade E46 M3, a masterclass in atmospheric induction. The S54B32 inline-six remains internally pristine, exhibiting robust oil pressure and a flawlessly quiet VANOS unit. The chassis has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including subframe reinforcement and a full refresh of the suspension kinematics. Every gear engagement through the Getrag manual is surgical, and the M-variable differential lock provides optimal torque vectoring. This vehicle is mechanically impeccable, free of any parasitic loss or thermal issues, representing the pinnacle of the analog driving era.",
